snippet.title: Courtshake
snippet.description:
I review movies and television series, and I rant about other geeky things. I also have a healthy appreciation for Batman. Subscribe to this channel for movie and TV reviews, both spoiler-free and spoiler-filled (no worries, you will be warned), as well as entertainment news coverage, trailer reactions, and other fun things.

Follow me! 

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/courtshake/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Courtshake
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/courtshake/
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/courtshake

Cheers!
